## What Needs Your Hardware Touch
You have the RTX 4050 machine — perfect for running yosys + nextpnr synthesis. The FCP Verilog needs:
1. Lattice iCE40 primitive mapping (SB_IO, SB_GB, BRAM)
2. Pin constraints for the eval board
3. Clock domain planning (16 MHz internal oscillator)

## The FCP+PAU Verilog Already Exists
- FCP: 4-stage pipeline, 12 hardwired opcodes, 22K gates — designed in CPA architecture doc
- PAU: 176-line Verilog module, 2-BRAM composition table, 196 MHz on iCE40 — TESTED
- P48 composition table: 48×48 entries in 288 bytes ROM — ready to synthesize

